videos.description: Avery Johnson Jr. snags the ball on an Arizona pass and drives it to the basket for a layup.
videos.headline: Alabama widens lead with Johnson steal and finish

videos.description: Arizona's Brandon Williams fakes a handoff and drives the ball to the basket himself to cut Alabama's lead to 64-62.
videos.headline: Williams sinks layup to close Alabama's lead
